name: imgroi
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "imgroi" %}
{% set version = "0.0.1" %}
{% set sha256 = "0d00021107f3131a1c2bbfae8bc94e0ffc04758544a48fe63743d455f7a8c415" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python
    - numpy
    - mahotas

test:
  imports:
    - imgroi

about:
  home: https://github.com/jakirkham/imgroi
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Python utility functions for slices.
  doc_url: https://imgroi.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/jakirkham/imgroi

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
